text: Patricia Couturier (born 1 January 1961) is a French rower. She competed in the women's quadruple sculls event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:French female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
